show.description: A mysterious woman takes her sister’s place in an arranged marriage to save her family. Behind her calm façade lies a past full of secrets, deception, and hidden strength. As she steps into a world of power, betrayal, and love, her true identity begins to unravel. Each revelation shakes the lives of those around her—and the man she was never meant to marry.
